title: Joe Rogan Experience Review of Andy Ngo
description:
JRE Review of 1323 with Andy Ngo

Andy Ngo is a reporter that was recently assulted at a protest rally in Portland. He discusses what happened with Joe and the potential dangers he see's with this kind of protest not being handled correctly by law enforcement. It was an eye opening conversation to review. Let me know what you got out of it!
